titles: Henricus Dominus Carye, Vicecomes Falklandiæ, contrarotulator hospitii serenissimi domini Regis Iacobi, deputatus suæ Maiestatis in Regno Hiberniæ & unus dominorum priuati consilii dicti domini regis in regno Angliæ
